code: @Override public int getRawStatusCode() throws IOException {     return this.nettyResponse.getStatus().code(). }
@Override public String getStatusText() throws IOException {     return this.nettyResponse.getStatus().reasonPhrase(). }

@Override public HttpHeaders getHeaders() {     HttpHeaders headers = this.headers.     if (headers == null) {         headers = new HttpHeaders().         for (Map.Entry<String, String> entry : this.nettyResponse.headers()) {             headers.add(entry.getKey(), entry.getValue()).         }         this.headers = headers.     }     return headers. }
@Override public InputStream getBody() throws IOException {     return this.body. }
